<L>__{ext rko lot day}
<A>__{welles is pursuing schaefer as they stride through the bustling rko backlot.}
<C>__{schaefer}
<D>__{what do you want me to do, orson? radio city won't premiere the picture. louella threatened them with some bullshit about}
